"{\"uid\": \"standard.co.uk-sport-football-paris-2024-olympics-football-draw-how-to-watch-tv-channel-live-stream-start-time-teams-today-b1146429.html\", \"text\": \"To use the search feature, we need your consent to load Google Custom Search, which may use cookies or similar technologies. Please click 'Allow and Continue' below to enable search. See our privacy policy for more information.  Sport|Football  The draw for the 2024Paris Olympicsis about to take place for both the men's and women's tournaments.  Brazil have failed to qualify to defend their men's gold medal while Canada are out to retain the women's crown, afterTeam GBmissed out on a spot due to their early exit from the Nations League.  A total of 16 teams will be split into four groups for the men's tournament while the women's will divide 12 teams into three groups, meaning the best two third-placed teams will qualify for the knockouts.  As per usual, the men'sOlympicsteams will be predominantly made up of players under the age of 23 with no restrictions on the women's squads.  TheOlympic footballdraw takes place tonight, Wednesday March 20, 2024 in the Pulse building which is the headquarters of the Paris Games.  It is set to begin a 7pm GMT.  Men's  Pot 1  Pot 2  Pot 3  Pot 4  Three Asian nations, plus a play-off between the fourth-placed team at the U23 Asian Cup and fourth-placed team at the U23 Africa Cup of Nations, Guinea, will decide the final four spots.  Women's  Pot 1  Pot 2  Pot 3  Pot 4  Two African nations will qualify in April's play-offs, which see South Africa face Nigeria and Zambia take on Morocco.  TV channel and live stream:The draw will be broadcast live and for free online via the FIFA+ streaming service.  The schedule is already set for both tournaments with the first group games being held on Wednesday, July 24 and Thursday, July 25. The men's final takes place on Friday, August 9 and the women's on Saturday, August 10.  MORE ABOUT  Have your say...  1  Crime  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line train after youths told to stop vaping by middle-aged passenger  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line after youths told to stop vaping  2  Football  Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup, confirmed team news, injury latest for Premier League today  Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup and confirmed team news  3  UK  Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning over Donald Trump's Iran war  Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning on Iran war  4  Lifestyle  Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026  Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026  5  Football  Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news, predicted lineup, injury latest for Carabao Cup final  Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news and predicted lineup\"}"